tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"秦吏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f0a6a56bd64aedc20c58ede474a9c0633eb21d","tid":2435193,"uid":39492,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"《赤裸裸的共產黨：共產主義如何危害自由世界》<br />\n好似一月時已經喺連登提過呢本書<br />\n不過睇得慢, 依家先就嚟睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原著(英文)第一次出版係喺1958年, 最新版好似係2017年<br />\n中文譯本就係喺2019年出版<br />\n<br />\n呢本書可以算係共產黨簡史, 有:<br />\n馬克思、恩格斯、列寧、史達林等人嘅生平<br />\n共產主義嘅概要: 起源、理論、謬誤<br />\n主要講蘇聯、美國之間嘅關係變化(二戰前、後)<br />\n討論1960年代, 共產黨提出過嘅45個目標, 如今有幾多已經達成咗 (其實只剩1個係未達成)<br />\n<br />\n我覺得睇唔慣史書嘅人都好啱睇, 文字表達得唔悶<br />\n同埋同自己息息相關, 你每睇每一段, 都可以令你諗到支共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb60feb476816c8f2764ab04b7dae847fb8eeba5","tid":2435193,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f29ee63f1598663d06a7030cae74fdb34cd72a","tid":2435193,"uid":219931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"Discourses of Epictetus"},{"pid":"5f2f95163067933dcf07be761ede74536916aadd","tid":2435193,"uid":138223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e079b63270babf1ec216087e480234fec0c0af8","tid":2435193,"uid":78466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"被討厭的勇氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:44:55.000Z","msg":"第一本好睇 第二開始一般<br />\n唔知第三本點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d379c1e9c80b5a387f6ce4ddd8c443cd4316d7","tid":2435193,"uid":251925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KQbXwS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KQbXwS.jpg&h=f74ef460&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93706f63785